### ─── Variables ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@apiKey = test-api-key-123

###
# ─── URL Shortener ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### Create a short link (auto-generated key)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "http://localhost:3000/resume?cfg=eJwlyEEOgjAQQNGrTP56YjpFC85ZurFBAzFBgwgLwt1N7Or9_J0VN2XAialDufc4G8r4xinPNqHM-E7A6a5mFq0xFMMxDuWDk78hBJM_sdLINi5D7bNWL5Wkcpv62q3kInmRx2uWPNVXThw_HBQmTw"
}

###

### Create a short link (custom key)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "sike",
  "url": "http://localhost:3000/resume?cfg=eJw9zrEOwjAMBNBfsTq7CBcG-hfsUQaTmjaiOJA4lP49AgTLSad7wzlCrfP8DXfAHomQOqQd0h6pRzr4_0gd9h6d2_7KB7-l9-gI3dd7j81xtSlpe06hFhnAMg9RRyhrMbkWEB2jimRYok0wp6Wd2UTDClHPmYvlGqxmAXneJEfRIMA6QLGcdIR7ZbVobPEhwNXSlS0mhROHy5hT1WHTfF77F94kSqs"
}

### 

### List all short links for authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Delete a short link
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten/mylink
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Test redirection (will 302 redirect to target)
GET {{baseUrl}}/r/resume

###

### Test redirection with version tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/r/resume?v=CampaignA

###

### Dynamic base64 redirector
# To generate the dest param: btoa("https://example.com") => "aHR0cHM6Ly9leGFtcGxlLmNvbQ=="
GET {{baseUrl}}/redirect?dest=aHR0cHM6Ly9leGFtcGxlLmNvbQ==&v=email_blast&id=cta_link

###
# ─── Analytics ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### Get all analytics events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics

###

### Filter analytics by targetId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics?targetId=resume

###

### Filter analytics by targetId and version
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics?targetId=resume&version=CampaignA

###

### Filter analytics by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics?type=redirect

###

### Filter analytics by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics?startDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z

###
# ─── Event Ingestion ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### Ingest a custom event (e.g. from SDK or server-side)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "custom",
  "name": "button_click",
  "targetId": "hero_cta",
  "sessionId": "sess_abc123",
  "url": "https://myapp.com/landing",
  "referrer": "https://google.com",
  "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Test)",
  "version": "v1",
  "metadata": {
    "buttonLabel": "Get Started"
  }
}

###
# ─── Pixel Tracker ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### Email pixel - track open (returns 1x1 GIF)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pixel/campaign_jan2026/recipient_alice.png

###

### Email pixel - without extension
GET {{baseUrl}}/pixel/campaign_jan2026?v=email_v2

###
# ─── Misc ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### Interactive demo page (open in browser instead for full experience)
GET {{baseUrl}}/demo

### SDK script (served statically)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sdk/sdk.js
